{
    "chapter": [
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "The pounding disaster"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "What is the pounding disaster"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "And do you know what the pounding disaster is"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "A day when the people become like scattered butterflies"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "and the mountains become like fluffed up colored wool"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "As for anyone whose balance (of good deeds) is heavy"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "then he is in a pleasant life"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "And as for anyone whose balance (of good deeds) is light"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "then his residence is a bottomless pit"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "And you don't even know what it is"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "(It is) a scorching fire"
        }
    ]
}